{"tid":720862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片：女客困試身室　消防爆門","createTime":"2018-06-28T09:03:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T09:03:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a50bdbc1aacd5277a262135879fc9cfa115ae7cc","tid":720862,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T09:03:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180628/20433881\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180628%2F20433881&d=ru7BXlD9JOrC8aP0jmFt%2FDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=3db6aab6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180628%2F20433881&h=4d9bcff1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180628/20433881</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月28日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：女客困試身室　消防爆門<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180628/large/a1104a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180628%2Flarge%2Fa1104a.gif&h=f8ba7538&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔理心情好壞，小記都會買衫，但如果試衫遇上被困試身室，真係掃興兼瘀到爆，好似噚日呢位女士咁，唔嬲豬就奇！<br />\n<br />\n讀者葉先生噚日下晝1點半左右，經過海港城一間連鎖時裝店，發現有大批消防員喺入面（圖），拎晒架生咁，亦有消防員喺一間試身室外邊圍晒膠紙，好大陣仗咁。「消防員同試身室入面嘅人講，陣間會爆門」，葉先生就知道，原來係有人被困喺試身室入面，「我聽到把女人聲，出面有位男士等緊佢」。<br />\n<br />\n葉先生喺門外企咗十分鐘，保安員終於拉起黑布，擋住試身室做嘢。葉認為呢啲咁瘀嘅事發生喺大型連鎖店，都真係匪夷所思。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片：無人駕駛「盲牛」老蘭亂鏟<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n今日焦點‧即聽"}]}